Description de la recherche=A0:
The research will be conducted within MIMOSA (MultIModal Ontolgy-driven
query system for the heterogeneous data of a
SmArtcity), a research project aiming at extending a participatory GIS
prototype platform, named "Mappe di Comunit=E0
3.0" with advanced information search facilities. The project concerns =
the
investigation of new approaches to enhance
query-driven data summarization by data factorization. In particular, it
will address the topic of multi-modal, multi-
relational and heterogeneous data factorization and clustering by
integrating different types of knowledge and information:
spatial information, text documents, images. Since factorization and
clustering algorithms should take into account the
particular query that a user is typing, the task will also involve
constraint-driven problems for data factorization in the
multimodal case.=A0


